                <note rend="inline" type="source">211.67/40a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Skinner</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-02-09T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 9, 1934—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. Senate on February 5 consented ratification treaty of extradition between
                    United States and Turkey, signed at Lausanne, Switzerland, August 6, 1923.
                    Inform Turkish Government. Cable status of treaty in Turkey.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
